sentences.english: Many believe that is posturing on Buck's part but Arsenal are digging their heels in.

sentences.english: The Arsenal manager wants to attack Villareal, playing to Arsenal's strengths of free-flowing attacking football.

sentences.english: Two hundred years ago, Ascension Island was a barren volcanic edifice.
